name: Fractals Instances 2 - Quad Orgy
description:
Interactive p5.js sketch. 

Controls : 
Click on screen: to generate fractal growth
B : Randomize COLORS
S : activate/deactivate border.

This is the second of a series on where you generate a particle that when it dies its spawns 2 particles repeating that like ten times. 

This is have lots quads. Enjoy
